{"id":"extended-diagnostics/NG8108","title":"NG8108: ngSkipHydration should be a static attribute","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n\n  <h1 id=\"ng8108-ngskiphydration-should-be-a-static-attribute\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5lezadeifvw5g3r7uvom0n614\">NG8108: ngSkipHydration should be a static attribute<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8108#ng8108-ngskiphydration-should-be-a-static-attribute\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n\n  <div class=\"diagnostic-description\">\n    <h2 id=\"description\">說明<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8108#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7zqh8wmy4v4pzpmabs8hde46t\"><code>ngSkipHydration</code> 是一個特殊的屬性，它告訴 Angular 不要讓某些特定元件參與水合。此診斷可確保靜態設定此屬性 <code>ngSkipHydration</code> 並將值設定為 <code>\"true\"</code> 或空值。</p>\n<h2 id=\"what-should-i-do-instead\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7bicb9bjjdedhs8bfd5vdiby7\">我該怎麼辦？<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"extended-diagnostics/NG8108#what-should-i-do-instead\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"5asoo4uj1e3frmkyw1lh0nidx\">使用 <code>ngSkipHydration</code> 時，請確保將其設定為靜態屬性（即不要使用 Angular 範本繫結語法）。</p>\n<code-example format=\"html\" language=\"html\">\n&lt;my-cmp ngSkipHydration /&gt;\n&lt;!-- or --&gt;\n&lt;my-cmp ngSkipHydration=\"true\" /&gt;\n</code-example>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1tl6suaasu3xo2b1onvdft0o9\">有關更多訊息，請參閱<a href=\"extended-diagnostics#configuration\">擴充套件診斷設定</a>。</p>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  </div>\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - extended-diagnostics\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - extended-diagnostics#configuration\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8108#description\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8108#ng8108-ngskiphydration-should-be-a-static-attribute\n - extended-diagnostics/NG8108#what-should-i-do-instead\n-->"}